{
  "stem": "6803.1",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And some SS-- I do remember.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "When they gave us a little water to drink, each one a little drink.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Some SS-- I realize, [? now ?] I looked at their faces, I think it was that impression that they felt sorry for us.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Some of them, yes.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Some of them, they did felt like sorry for us.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Why?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So anyway, so we left that station.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we headed up to Mauthausen.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We got off the train.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Of course the SS were waiting for us.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We didn't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We-- we didn't know what.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we saw when we got into the camp, it says Mauthausen Arbeit macht frei, was written up there.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Free.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the SS, aufgehen!",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Aufgehen!",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Aufgehen!",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We were not supposed to look on the side.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We were not supposed to see anything.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Just from the station.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "From the station, go into the car-- into the camp car, the Mauthausen.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we were scattered around the streets around the camp.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I remember that, too.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "It was evening.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And then-- and one SS man came with a German Shepherd.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I remember that, too.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Quite frankly, I remember that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And he started to say to that dog, [SPEAKING GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And a man there, a Jewish man, I don't know who the man is.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And he started to grab here.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "The man tried to pull away himself.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "He couldn't.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "The more he pulled, the more he ripped his flesh out.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He called the dog that-- he is the mench, and the mench is the dog.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You see what I mean?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So that's what I remember that, too.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I was standing there, and I'm looking at myself.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I look at him.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I says, [? that, ?] why?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Look at this here.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the SS stands there.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
